====Noun/Verb/Adjective/Adverb====
# '''Jaun'''
In the same sense of '''meef''', Jaun can be used as anything, a global variable of sorts.  For Example:
"Give me that '''jaun''' before I '''jaun''' you in the face with my '''jaun''' like a '''jaun'''!
or "You see that jawn over there... i'm bout to holla at that jawn... take her back to my jawn, ya'mean."
